						<summary>

						<p>Hero-stone set up near the Basavaṇṇa temple.</p>						

						<p>A.D. 1159.</p>						

						<p>This badly damaged record is dated in Śaka 10[81], Pramāthin, Mā[rgaśira] śu. 11, Monday corresponding A.D. 1159, November 23, Monday.</p>						

						<p>Seems to record the death of a chief in a cattle-raid. <hi rend="italic">Manneya</hi> Nāgaṇa probably set up the stone.</p>						

						</summary>
